            "creation_date": 1434605837,
            "body": "<p>If you have a class of <code>JMath<\/code> and you want to get all its objects on runtime(Dynamically allocation) then you just wrote<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>ArrayList&lt;JMath&gt; J = new ArrayList&lt;JMath&gt; ();\n<\/code><\/pre>\n",
            "answer_id": 30907233,
